      <div class="col-md-8 left-col">
         <div class="row">
            <div class="col blog-header">
                  <div class="title-area">
                     <div class="post-info">
                        <p class="post-date">23rd February 2018</p>
                        <p>/</p>
                        <p class="category"><ul class="post-categories">
	<li><a href="https://astonservicesgroup.co.uk/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a></li></ul></p>
                     </div>
                     <h1 class="post-title">New Director of Industrial Cleaning and Maintenance</h1>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         <div class="row image-row">
            <div class="col">
               <div class="post-image">
                                       <div style="background-image: url('https://astonservicesgroup.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/img-f6a2fb55b8b74ac51cdd634937055336.jpg')"></div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
               <div class="content post-content">
                  <div>
<div class="news-article__summary">
<p>Aston Services Group welcomes Phil Todd!</p>
</div>
<div class="news-article__content">
<p>We are delighted to announce that Phil Todd has joined Aston Services Group as Director of the Industrial and Maintenance divisions. Phil, previously a Director of W. Whiteside Ltd. (an established reactive maintenance company operating throughout the North West), brings an impressive knowledge of the sector and his recruitment is a testament to the continued growth and aspirations of the group.</p>
<p>Phil commented, “With my background in the leisure and retail sectors, I feel that the opportunity to join Aston is culturally an excellent fit. I am genuinely excited to be a part of the continued growth and success of this forward-thinking group.”</p>
</div>
</div>
